<div class="thumbinner" style="width:292px;"><a href="/wiki/File:MSF_instructor.jpg" class="image" title="A novice rider receives coaching in an MSF course"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f0/MSF_instructor.jpg/290px-MSF_instructor.jpg" width="290" height="199" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
