<p><b>Motorcycle safety</b> concerns many aspects of vehicle and equipment design as well as operator skill and training that are unique to <a href="/wiki/Motorcycle" title="Motorcycle">motorcycle</a> riding.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
